description:
Learn to identify valuable collectibles by brand. This must-have collection of 12+ porcelain apps, 80+ styles, 8,000+ best-of-the-best images, 6,000+ videos, 5,000+ 3D pages, and 10 volumes of displaced paper provides designers, discerning homemakers, sellers, artisans, and porcelain collectors with the most complete coverage - all on your phone. 

These apps are evergreen - self-improving with crowd-sourced best-of-the-best images, articles, and videos collected from thousands on the web. Indulge your love of porcelain, this app collection is magical.
